des:
Novahome products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to control your home device.
After connecting Alexa to your Novahome products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our Novahome app in android or iOS app market;
(2). Register your account in our Novahome app;
(3). You need to have some Novahome devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our Novahome app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in Novahome skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, iOS or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search Novahome skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of Novahome, and you'll be navigated to Novahome login page;
(9). Input your Novahome account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa, set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white."
